{"tid":2112981,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台友好]有香港人參與其中嘅台灣成人遊戲","createTime":"2020-07-17T18:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T01:55:24.000Z","uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca38be8fc1292c6101b0978886c7ef701db8168f","tid":2112981,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T18:37:05.000Z","msg":"其實只係佔咗一小部分，不過最近完成咗上架STEAM所以都貼吓。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由一班<del>台妹港女</del>加埋個台仔老闆制作嘅成人遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係我無寫錯，唔講唔知，<br />\n原來連成人遊戲都唔係毒撚自給自足。<br />\n反而唔少部分係成班女女做出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝各位一支公都有個幸福嘅夜晚。<br />\n<br />\nSteam Link(成人限定，需登入)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1333360/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1333360%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=0b22923f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1333360/</a><br />\n<br />\n【故事簡介】<br />\n格倫是一名視財如命的奴隸商人，在一次拍賣會中拍下了前貴族奎涅爾家族的千金克菈蒂雅。為了重獲自由，克菈蒂雅締結了替格倫賺足金錢便能贖身的約定，毅然決然地踏入險惡的鬥技場，她所面臨的將是勝者的榮耀、家族的復興，亦或者是受盡屈辱的地獄？而隨著神祕暗精靈艾琳的加入，三人間又將掀起一場臉紅心跳的大風波&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n【遊戲玩法】<br />\n本遊戲設有多重結局，透過不同條件可觸發多種H劇情，劇情選項及鬥技場勝負結果將影響遊戲的走向，因此玩家需謹慎分配每日行動點數，透過調教或訓練來養成美麗的角鬥士們，並藉由委託及鬥技比賽賺取收入。<br />\n <br />\n【遊戲特色】<br />\n多達10萬字的劇情文本。<br />\n豐富的H劇情、事件。（250+ CG枚數、25+事件數.）<br />\n風格截然不同的雙女主角路線，對應複數結局的多元走向。<br />\n簡單明快的養成模式，刺激的戰鬥體驗。<br />\n隨心所欲養成及調教自己的角鬥士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係嗰句，唔好相認好撚老尷。"},{"pid":"c50fa1f93925041cd0bc15b51510d48e67845be4","tid":2112981,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"傷風敗德<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />此風不可長"},{"pid":"62f5ededc0584fbda0c22c82337d7f0d53331f83","tid":2112981,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:30:22.000Z","msg":"女性向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a354cd33c2f06b84b43b2e2aeecfcc531db7ac","tid":2112981,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f5ededc0584fbda0c22c82337d7f0d53331f83","tid":2112981,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:30:22.000Z","msg":"女性向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"男性向，男主人翁+幾靚仔。"},{"pid":"20c729091ac75772c792e328add86800b82e40d3","tid":2112981,"uid":114094,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"港台人整game 大撚曬？用呢樣野黎sale 睇黎你隻game 都係得咁上下"}]}